462
00:28:58,739 --> 00:29:00,115
Je sais. Tu as raison.

463
00:29:06,371 --> 00:29:07,539
C'est quoi, ces trucs-là?

464
00:29:10,167 --> 00:29:11,168
Où?

465
00:29:17,174 --> 00:29:19,676
Une heure. Vers l'est.

466
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:22,429
