- Non.

467
00:29:22,513 --> 00:29:24,056
Pas de nageoires.

468
00:29:25,015 --> 00:29:26,225
Des voiles.

469
00:29:35,234 --> 00:29:37,444
Bella, prends la barre.

470
00:29:47,037 --> 00:29:48,580
Gauche, gauche, gauche.

471
00:29:56,588 --> 00:29:57,798
