657
00:41:23,734 --> 00:41:25,444
C'est beau!

658
00:41:26,028 --> 00:41:27,029
Oui!

659
00:41:28,238 --> 00:41:29,239
Allons-y!

660
00:41:38,624 --> 00:41:39,625
On la perd.

661
00:41:47,049 --> 00:41:49,927
Loomis, sécurisez-moi
